MOU_LBD
=======

   These functions simulate left button down and up.

MOU_LBD
     Send a left button down.

MOU_LBU
     Send a left button up.


@EndNode

@Node "MOU_MBD" "MachV.guide/MOU_MBD"
@Next "MOU_RBD"
@Prev "MOU_LBD"
@Toc "Macro Functions"

MOU_MBD
=======

   These functions simulate middle button down and up.

MOU_MBD
     Send a middle button down.

MOU_MBU
     Send a middle button up.


@EndNode

@Node "MOU_RBD" "MachV.guide/MOU_RBD"
@Next "MOU_XY"
@Prev "MOU_MBD"
